Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.39,0:02:42.57,default - cyan - with - background,,0,0,0,,あいつがまた帰ってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.39,0:02:42.57,Default - white - with - background,,0,0,0,,He's come back again
