Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:52.78,Default - white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(511.195,506.723)}Akagi Shigeru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.39,0:02:59.77,default - cyan - with - background,,0,0,0,,誰の肩に止まるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.39,0:02:59.77,Default - white - with - background,,0,0,0,,Whose shoulder will it land upon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.77,0:03:05.77,default - cyan - with - background,,0,0,0,,くるくる廻る天道虫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.77,0:03:05.77,Default - white - with - background,,0,0,0,,Ladybug going round and round
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.77,0:03:10.13,default - cyan - with - background,,0,0,0,,背中の星が揃ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.77,0:03:10.13,Default - white - with - background,,0,0,0,,When the stars on her back align
