Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.13,0:03:20.04,Default - white - with - background,,0,0,0,,After the rain, above the windswept street,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.11,0:03:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(644.026,87.227)}#/tv/shows subs: "They're better than nothing!"
