Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.39,0:22:47.12,small - white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(963.623,116.094)}East Team:\NTen: {\c&H00FF00&}49000{\c&HFFFFFF&} Hiroyuki: {\c&H0000FF&}1000
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.50,0:22:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(639.195,581.834)}this is an expression of our determination
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.37,0:22:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(638.389,599.19)}Without averting our eyes from hard facts,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.80,0:22:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,embrace each crisis while moving forward,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.27,0:22:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Opening the way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.59,0:23:02.81,Default - white,,0,0,0,,{\s1}SanAnKou{\s0}\NChitoitsu\NChanta\NSanSyoku\NIttsu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.49,0:23:07.49,Default - white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(656.906,596.093)}East Round 2
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.71,0:23:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(637.988,583.362)}An awful starting hand, well beyond saving
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.17,0:23:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If he discards a South wind, the hand will not continue
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.63,0:24:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you retreat from such a position?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.33,0:24:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Advance!
